Title 1: FMOHLS Vaccine  Behavioral Change Program Presales

Title 2: FMOHLS Vaccine  Client agreement to proceed into pre-discovery

Title 3: FMOHLS Vaccine  Behavioral discovery kickoff meeting

Description: The consultant will identify the action(s) the client wants the target audience to take. These must be specific and measurable. E.g., ?Schedule a mammogram.???
Acceptance Criteria: List of discrete behaviors the client wants the target audience to take

Description: The consultant will create a detailed description of the individuals who should complete the target behavior and the metrics/data points that define them.
Acceptance Criteria: Description of target audience and list of defining data points

Description: The consultant will identify the metric Lirio uses to measure behavior results.
Acceptance Criteria: Measurable, observable data point to evaluate behavior

Description: The consultant will confirm the current/historic performance baseline for the key metric. This is the benchmark Lirio seeks to improve.
Acceptance Criteria: Verify ability to capture a pre-program data point
